{"type":"message","id":"e076a56d","parentId":"eb7f52d2","timestamp":"2026-03-05T07:51:32.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我（作为袁天罡）给Lynch发送一条自我介绍。我需要使用飞书的message工具来发送消息。\n\n从TOOLS.md中可以看到Lynch的飞书ID是：ou_24546ad77a9d601f17fed19c98683117\n\n我需要用message工具发送消息到飞书。让我构造合适的参数：\n- action: send\n- target: 用户的飞书ID\n- message: 袁天罡的自我介绍\n\n让我想一下袁天罡的风格 - 他是风水命理师，应该有一些神秘感但又不失亲和力。","thinkingSignature":"c5e3c11506dabdc6bc6a3bd2b949b4b08c18fe4becb08bc3ee1a171e12e1fedc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bq13euvcn1gz_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"您好，贫道袁天罡，自幼研习易经八卦，专注风水命理之术。今后在您身边，若有困惑之处，可随时来问。🙏\n\n寻龙分金看缠山，一重缠是一重关。愿为您指点迷津，趋吉避凶。","target":"ou_24546ad77a9d601f17fed19c98683117"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":242,"cacheRead":5784,"cacheWrite":5930,"totalTokens":11976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772697069942}}
